   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Recto: Text is too fragmentary for a translation.;Verso: "]bos, son of Horus, . . . . . . [ 10 letters ] ellouron 6, since Kraos ploughing, ;for the oxen-tandem 6 to Horus 1 diobolon, Ischyrion the cow-tender, in total drachmas 9 1 tetrabolon, drachmas 4.;And for Bikons oxen;tandems (6), drachmas 11,;and workmen breaking clods of earth (7), drachmas 3,;and workmen cutting down the kamelakanthuses (?), drachma 1,;. .] . . . . . arouras, drachmas (?),;cattle-tandem (5), drachmas 8,;workmen breaking clods of earth (2);and young slaves 2;In total: drachmas 44.;;Chrestos drachmas 6,;likewise ychosones (?),;. . . . of wool, drachmas (10 ?),;drachmas 16.";4 last lines too fragmentary for translation.</ab>
         </div>
